<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:15:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>官方媒体称，200多名中国公民从黎巴嫩撤离</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/more-than-200-chinese-citizens-evacuated-lebanon-state-media-says-2024-10-02/</link><description>据中国官方新华社周三报道，黎巴嫩政府已安全撤离200多名中国公民。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 08:54:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/more-than-200-chinese-citizens-evacuated-lebanon-state-media-says-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>即将离任的戴姆勒卡车首席执行官认为中国和德国没有复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/outgoing-daimler-truck-ceo-sees-no-recovery-china-germany-2024-10-02/</link><description>全球最大卡车制造商戴姆勒卡车即将卸任的首席执行官马丁·道姆 (Martin Daum) 在周二晚间的新闻发布会上表示，中国和德国卡车市场的复苏不会很快到来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 08:48:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/outgoing-daimler-truck-ceo-sees-no-recovery-china-germany-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>官员称，通过台湾海峡的德国船只已被警告驶离</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/german-ships-that-passed-through-taiwan-strait-were-warned-off-officials-say-2024-10-02/</link><description>德国特遣小组指挥官周三表示，上个月穿越台湾海峡的德国海军舰艇受到了中国船只的密切监视和重复无线电信息，但没有出现不安全行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/german-ships-that-passed-through-taiwan-strait-were-warned-off-officials-say-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>南海紧张局势下，菲律宾吸引国防公司进行军事现代化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/philippines-draws-defence-firms-military-modernises-amid-south-china-sea-tension-2024-10-02/</link><description>在南中国海紧张局势加剧之际，菲律宾正在启动最新阶段的耗资数十亿美元的军事现代化计划，全球国防承包商展示了他们的先进硬件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:53:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/philippines-draws-defence-firms-military-modernises-amid-south-china-sea-tension-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>IEA表示，氢能项目投资正在加速，但不确定性仍然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/hydrogen-project-investments-are-accelerating-uncertainty-remains-iea-says-2024-10-02/</link><description>国际能源署 (IEA) 在周三的一份报告中表示，过去 12 个月，氢项目的最终投资决定增加了一倍，其中以中国为主，但由于该行业面临不确定性，装机容量和需求较低。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 05:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/hydrogen-project-investments-are-accelerating-uncertainty-remains-iea-says-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警首次进入北极与俄罗斯联合巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-coast-guard-enters-arctic-first-time-patrol-with-russia-2024-10-02/</link><description>据官方媒体周三报道，中国海警船队首次进入北冰洋，与俄罗斯海警船队进行联合巡逻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 04:46:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-coast-guard-enters-arctic-first-time-patrol-with-russia-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>美元走强导致金价下跌；美国数据关注美联储降息线索</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-prices-flat-dollar-strength-counters-safe-haven-demand-2024-10-02/</link><description>由于美元坚挺，金价周三下跌，而投资者则寻求更多美国经济数据，以进一步了解美联储即将降息的迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 04:02:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-prices-flat-dollar-strength-counters-safe-haven-demand-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>中东紧张局势对市场影响不大，股市稳定，油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-02/</link><description>周三大多数股市坚挺，而油价和一些避险资产上涨，表明中东紧张局势升级对市场的影响目前已得到遏制。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 01:30:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>台湾因台风“Krathon”停工，带来暴雨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-shuts-down-ahead-typhoon-krathons-arrival-torrential-rain-forecast-2024-10-02/</link><description>台湾周三关闭，数百架航班停飞，学校、办公室和金融市场关闭，随后台风“克拉松”即将到来，据报道造成一人死亡，台湾南部遭遇暴雨。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 00:45:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-shuts-down-ahead-typhoon-krathons-arrival-torrential-rain-forecast-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国财政部官员称国际货币基金组织对中国政策和融资保证“过于礼貌”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/imf-too-polite-china-policies-financing-assurances-us-treasury-official-says-2024-10-01/</link><description>美国财政部一位高级官员周二表示，国际货币基金组织在批评中国经济政策时“过于客气”，应更全面地披露中国和其他一些国家为支持国际货币基金组织贷款计划而提供的融资保证。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 22:32:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/imf-too-polite-china-policies-financing-assurances-us-treasury-official-says-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：伊朗和以色列紧张局势引发市场下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-10-01/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 21:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔希拉尔击败阿尔肖塔，阿尔艾因在亚洲冠军联赛中失利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-hilal-down-al-shorta-al-ain-lose-asian-champions-league-2024-10-01/</link><description>周二，阿尔希拉尔在利雅得以 5-0 击败伊拉克的阿尔肖塔，与沙特职业联赛球队阿尔阿赫利一起在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛的两场比赛中获得最高分，卫冕冠军阿尔艾因以 4-2 输给阿尔阿赫利-加拉法。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 21:11:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-hilal-down-al-shorta-al-ain-lose-asian-champions-league-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔兹证实，天安门抗议期间他在美国，而不是亚洲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/walz-was-us-not-asia-during-tiananmen-protests-minnesota-radio-reports-2024-10-01/</link><description>民主党副总统候选人蒂姆·沃尔兹 (Tim Walz) 在 1989 年天安门广场镇压期间并不像他所说的那样在香港或亚洲，明尼苏达州公共广播电台发现了当时与他的说法相矛盾的照片和报纸报道后，他于周二晚证实了这一点。索赔。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 20:44:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/walz-was-us-not-asia-during-tiananmen-protests-minnesota-radio-reports-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>意大利 Brembo 出售倍耐力股份，Tronchetti 旗下 Camfin 增持股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-brembo-starts-sale-56-pirelli-stake-2024-10-01/</link><description>布雷博 (Brembo) 以约 2.83 亿欧元（合 3.13 亿美元）的价格出售了其在轮胎制造商倍耐力 (Pirelli) 所持的全部 5.6% 股份，此举平息了有关这两家意大利集团合并的猜测。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 17:22:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-brembo-starts-sale-56-pirelli-stake-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>柬埔寨表示欢迎美国海军在中国的帮助下扩大港口规模</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodia-says-it-would-welcome-us-navy-port-expanded-with-chinas-help-2024-10-01/</link><description>柬埔寨周二表示，欢迎美国海军访问其云朗海军基地，五角大楼担心该基地将成为中国的前哨基地。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 17:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodia-says-it-would-welcome-us-navy-port-expanded-with-chinas-help-2024-10-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>